Class MappedDICOMObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.utils.DICOMObject
      • pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.utils.MappedDICOMObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>

    public class MappedDICOMObject
extends DICOMObject
    Simple implementation of the a memory mapped DICOM Object. This class provides no structural index, therefore, operations other than retrieving attributes by their full path may be slow.
